name: Missouri State Treasurer Scott Fitzpatrick
tweet: Last week, our #UnclaimedProperty team found almost 30k British pennies and half pennies in a safe deposit box from #KCMO. It took 5 staffers over 7 hours to sort, count, and bag them all. What will you find at  https://t.co/oojKveFwoq?  https://t.co/URLsKPWXi5
